with passing years.

00:01:20.100 --> 00:01:27.066 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But ears will hear
when music plays.

00:01:27.066 --> 00:01:33.364 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And eyes will see
each brand new day.

